com.adobe.creativesdk.foundation.storage

Class AdobeUXAssetBrowser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.adobe.creativesdk.foundation.storage.AdobeUXAssetBrowser

  • public class AdobeUXAssetBrowser
extends java.lang.Object
    AdobeUXAssetBrowser invokes the Adobe Creative Cloud Asset Browser UI component.

    AdobeUXAssetBrowser allows clients to browse for and select assets and have them returned as AdobeAsset instances.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes

      static class  AdobeUXAssetBrowser.ResultProvider

                      throws com.adobe.creativesdk.foundation.internal.utils.AdobeCSDKException
        Displays the Creative Cloud Asset Browser UI component for viewing and selecting Adobe Creative Cloud assets. The Asset Browser pops up as an Activity.
        Parameters:
        activity - the Activity that will receive the result in its onActivityResult() callback method. Look at the AdobeUXAssetBrowser.ResultProvider class for how to retrieve selection results.
        requestCode - the request code to use in the Intent for launching the Asset Browser Activity.
